OL,7,FA grieving widow said a former
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police volunteer who
OL,9,Fwas jailed for 12 months after
OL,10,Faccessing video footage of her
OL,11,Fhusband's body as he lay dying in the
OL,12,Fstreet and taking photos of it "took
OL,13,Fhis dignity" when he was at his most
OL,14,Fvulnerable.
