OL,4,Caccessed video of dying man and took
OL,5,Cphotos of it
OL,7,FThe former special constable volunteer
OL,8,FWilliam Heggs, 23, was said to have
OL,9,Fbeen an "exemplary" officer until it
OL,10,Fwas discovered he had taken
OL,11,Fphotographs on his personal phone from
OL,12,Fbody-worn footage of 28-year-old
OL,13,FWilliam Harty as he lay fatally
OL,14,Finjured in Bedale Drive, Leicester, on
OL,15,FOctober 25 2021.
OL,17,FHeggs, of Copeland Avenue, Leicester,
OL,18,Fhad attended the scene then aged 20
OL,19,Fand gave CPR to Mr Harty, but he died
OL,20,Fin hospital the next day having
OL,21,Fsuffered head injuries.
