OL,7,FMr Harty's brother-in-law Martin Casey
OL,8,Fwas later convicted of his
OL,9,Fmanslaughter.
OL,11,FA police investigation was launched
OL,12,Fafter he showed images he had taken
OL,13,Ffrom the body-worn footage of Mr
OL,14,FHarty's body and stored on his
OL,15,FSnapchat account to a colleague who
OL,16,Fsaid she did not like seeing blood.
