OL,7,FLeicester Crown Court heard Heggs, who
OL,8,Fwas suspended from the force until he
OL,9,Fresigned in October last year, said:
OL,10,F"I know I shouldn't have", as he
OL,11,Fshowed her the graphic pictures.
OL,13,FThe colleague reported him to his line
OL,14,Fmanager, which led to an investigation
OL,15,Fthat uncovered a number of other
OL,16,Foffences.
