OL,7,FMr Harty's widow Mandy Casey was in
OL,8,Fcourt on Friday as Heggs was jailed
OL,9,Ffor 12 months after admitting 11
OL,10,Fcomputer misuse and data protection
OL,11,Foffences, including securing
OL,12,Funauthorised access to data and
OL,13,Frecklessly obtaining or disclosing
OL,14,Fpersonal data.
