OL,7,FWhen Heggs's phone was seized by
OL,8,Fofficers, they found he had
OL,9,F"repeatedly and flagrantly" breached
OL,10,Fpolicing rules of which he would have
OL,11,Fbeen fully aware due to extensive
OL,12,Ftraining, prosecutor Cathlyn Orchard
OL,13,Ftold the court.
