OL,4,Caccessed video of dying man and took
OL,5,Cphotos of it
OL,7,FOver a period of six months between
OL,8,FJuly and December 2021, Heggs shared
OL,9,Fgraphic details of the injuries
OL,10,Fsuffered by a woman who had died in a
OL,11,Froad traffic collision to a Snapchat
OL,12,Fcontact, had shared body-worn footage
OL,13,Fof a fellow police officer falling
OL,14,Fover with another colleague and
OL,15,Flaughed about it, and had taken
OL,16,Fphotographs and videos which involved
OL,17,Fa knife seizure, use of a baton and
OL,18,Fpepper spray, and a man with an
OL,19,Finjured hand receiving first aid.
