OL,3,CJail for special constable who
OL,4,Caccessed video of dying man and took
OL,5,Cphotos of it
OL,7,FHe had also taken a photograph showing
OL,8,Fdetails of a man who had been
OL,9,Fconvicted of a sexual offence,
OL,10,Fincluding his date of birth, and 12
OL,11,Fphotographs of a police computer
OL,12,Fscreen on his personal mobile phone,
OL,13,Fwhich showed details of various crimes
OL,14,Fand suspects, without consent.
OL,16,FThe former volunteer, who joined the
OL,17,Fforce part-time in January 2021 as he
OL,18,Fstudied for a policing degree at De
OL,19,FMontfort University, kept the photos
OL,20,Fand videos in a Snapchat folder called
OL,21,F"My eyes only".
