OL,7,FThere is nothing to suggest he shared
OL,8,Fthem with anyone on social media, but
OL,9,Fhe did admit showing his mother one of
OL,10,Fthe photographs.
OL,12,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,13,Fthe court, Ms Casey said she had lost
OL,14,Ftrust in the police and remained
OL,15,Fscared that she might see photographs
OL,16,Fof her husband's body appearing on
OL,17,Fsocial media.
OL,19,F"He took my husband's dignity when he
OL,20,Fwas most vulnerable."
