OL,4,Caccessed video of dying man and took
OL,5,Cphotos of it
OL,7,FShe said: "You don't take someone's
OL,8,Fdignity and pride from them on their
OL,9,Fdeathbed."
OL,11,FMs Casey added: "He took my husband's
OL,12,Fdignity when he was most vulnerable.
OL,13,FWhen I found out special constable
OL,14,FHeggs had done this, I just wanted to
OL,15,Fask why.
OL,17,F"He has traumatised me. I feel I will
OL,18,Fnever know if he showed them to
OL,19,Fothers."
