OL,7,FJudge Timothy Spencer said Heggs, who
OL,8,Fhas autism and ADHD, was "probably too
OL,9,Fimmature to be working as a police
OL,10,Fofficer" as he jailed him for 12
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FHe said: "It is clear you did not lack
OL,14,Fenthusiasm and your policing was, at
OL,15,Ftimes, of an exemplary standard, but
OL,16,Fyou lacked maturity.
