OL,4,Caccessed video of dying man and took
OL,5,Cphotos of it
OL,7,F"You had received extensive training,
OL,8,Fyou knew the importance of data
OL,9,Fprotection and knew you should only
OL,10,Fshare materials for a genuine policing
OL,11,Fpurpose.
OL,13,F"You knew the lines were drawn and the
OL,14,Flines were very clear."
OL,16,FHe said Heggs, who appeared in the
OL,17,Fdock wearing a dark suit and white
OL,18,Fshirt with pink tie and looked ahead
OL,19,Fas he was sentenced, had carried out
OL,20,F"repeated and persistent breaches of
OL,21,Fwell-understood boundaries".
