OL,4,Caccessed video of dying man and took
OL,5,Cphotos of it
OL,7,FJudge Spencer accepted that Heggs's
OL,8,Factions were not out of "wickedness",
OL,9,Fbut said the defendant's claims that
OL,10,Fhe accessed the material so he could
OL,11,Flearn from the experience and become a
OL,12,Fbetter officer were "far-fetched".
OL,14,FHe said Heggs's actions had
OL,15,F"significantly undermined" public
OL,16,Ftrust and confidence in the police.
OL,18,FThe judge added: "You have a raft of
OL,19,Fexcellent references and your on-the-
OL,20,Fground policing was, at times,
OL,21,Fabsolutely exemplary.
