OL,7,F"You could have been a huge asset to
OL,8,Fthe police and to society. There is so
OL,9,Fmuch good in you and it is such a
OL,10,Ftragedy that you have thrown what
OL,11,Fcould have been a really good career
OL,12,Faway."
OL,14,FMembers of Heggs's family sobbed in
OL,15,Fthe public gallery as he was led down
OL,16,Fto the cells.
