OL,7,FMalcolm McHaffie, Head of the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service's Special Crime
OL,9,FDivision, said after the sentencing:
OL,10,F"William Heggs abused the public's
OL,11,Ftrust in the office he held as a
OL,12,Fspecial police constable.
OL,14,F"He violated the dignity of the
OL,15,Fdeceased victims for no apparent
OL,16,Freason other than what could be
OL,17,Fconsidered personal fascination and to
OL,18,Fgain credibility among his peers.
