OL,7,F"He repeatedly misused his authority
OL,8,Fto access police computers and
OL,9,Fflagrantly breached data protection
OL,10,Flaw in disclosing personal data to
OL,11,Fmembers of the public.
OL,13,F"He was not authorised to take
OL,14,Fphotographs of body-worn footage on
OL,15,Fhis personal mobile phone nor share
OL,16,Fthat footage with third parties. His
OL,17,Factions were insensitive and illegal.
